            <title>小米 2999 元米家空调健康风 1.5 匹开售：物理双柔风 + 离子净化技术，国补 2399.2 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/873/256.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/873/256.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 12:39:34 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
